Help for MODE:

Syntax: MODE <#channel> <mode> [parameters]

MODE allows for the editing of modes on a channel. Some networks
will most likely find this command to be unethical.

Examples:
    /msg &nick& MODE #heh -m
    /msg &nick& MODE #heh +o foo

Syntax: MODE ALL <mode> [parameters]

MODE can also set modes on all channels. This may be useful in
the event of a bot flood, to set all channels +R.

Examples:
    /msg &nick& MODE ALL +R
    /msg &nick& MODE ALL +M
